# Remotion-only assets — Remotion's `staticFile()` resolves from public/
# during local renders, but the deployed Next app never serves bg-music.mp3
# (verified via grep: 0 client/app references). Keeping 3.7 MB out of the
# Vercel-deployed bundle saves egress.
public/audio/bg-music.mp3
